INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS


SnOB is distributed in source format. It is assumed that the user i sufficiently 
familiar with his/her computing environment that he/she is  able to compile C++ 
source code into object code and executables.


THE SnOB CORE LIBRARY 

To compile the core SnOB classes, enter the src directory and issue the command 

make all



THE EXAMPLES

To compile the examples featured in the user manual, enter the examples directory 
and issue the command

make all

